OL,3,CThree more charged with murdering
OL,4,Cfather-of-two
OL,6,FThree more men have been charged with
OL,7,Fmurdering a father-of-two who died
OL,8,Fafter being chased and attacked.
OL,10,FSuhail Choudry, 35, was found with
OL,11,Fserious head injuries in Flasby
OL,12,FStreet, Keighley, in the early hours
OL,13,Fof Sunday, 8 February.
OL,15,FHe was taken to hospital, where he
OL,16,Fdied three days later.
OL,18,FWest Yorkshire Police said initial
OL,19,Fenquiries suggested he had been chased
OL,20,Fbefore being attacked with weapons
OL,21,Fincluding sticks and bats.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
