OL,3,CThree more charged with murdering
OL,4,Cfather-of-two
OL,6,FMohammed Aliyan Khan, 23, Faisal Khan,
OL,7,F26, both of Malsis Road, and Hakeem
OL,8,FGulzar, 27, of Plover Street, have all
OL,9,Fbeen charged with murder, possession
OL,10,Fof an offensive weapon in a public
OL,11,Fplace and violent disorder.
OL,13,FThey are due to appear at Bradford
OL,14,FMagistrates Court on Tuesday.
OL,16,FRashid Hussain, 41, of Redcliffe
OL,17,FStreet, has already been charged with
OL,18,Fmurder.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
