OL,3,CThree more charged with murdering
OL,4,Cfather-of-two
OL,6,FPolice said another man, aged 36, has
OL,7,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of
OL,8,Fassisting an offender and a 26-year-
OL,9,Fold woman has been arrested on
OL,10,Fsuspicion of conspiracy to commit
OL,11,Fmurder.
